summary: The document serves as a receipt for authentication materials, specifically Cuban documents, received under a certain memo number and date. It details the process for returning these materials to TSD/IB post-use and mandates notification to TSD/IB should any materials be destroyed or lost.
key_findings: Acknowledgement of receipt of authentication materials.
Details on the procedure for returning unused or no longer needed authentication materials to TSD/IB.
Instructions to notify TSD/IB in case of destruction or loss of materials.
